<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q11_v15" title="Q11_v15" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En una fábrica se utiliza la siguiente fórmula para calcular el costo total de producción en pesos chilenos:</p>
    <div>
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mi>C</m:mi>
          <m:mo>=</m:mo>
          <m:mn>4800</m:mn>
          <m:mo>·</m:mo>
          <m:mi>u</m:mi>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      <p>tal que <m:math><m:mi>u</m:mi></m:math> es el número de unidades fabricadas y <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi></m:math> es el costo total en pesos chilenos.</p>
    </div>
    <p>Para transformar pesos chilenos a dólares estadounidenses, se sabe que</p>
    <p>
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>1</m:mn>
          <m:mtext> dólar estadounidense</m:mtext>
          <m:mo>=</m:mo>
          <m:mn>800</m:mn>
          <m:mtext> pesos chilenos</m:mtext>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
    </p>
    <p>¿Cuál es el costo, en dólares, de fabricar <m:math><m:mn>150</m:mn></m:math> unidades?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">576&#160;000&#160;000 dólares<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Para 150 unidades, el costo en pesos es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4800</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>150</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>720&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos. Luego, como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext> dólar</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>800</m:mn><m:mtext> pesos</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>, el costo en dólares es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>720&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>800</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> dólares. Por lo tanto, 576&#160;000&#160;000 dólares no corresponde al problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">900 dólares<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Para 150 unidades, el costo total es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4800</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>150</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>720&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext> dólar estadounidense</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>800</m:mn><m:mtext> pesos chilenos</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math>, se convierte <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>720&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>800</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Entonces, fabricar 150 unidades cuesta 900 dólares.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">720&#160;000 dólares<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El valor 720&#160;000 corresponde al costo en pesos chilenos, porque <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4800</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>150</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>720&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos. Pero el problema pide el costo en dólares. Al convertir, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>720&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>800</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> dólares. Por eso, 720&#160;000 dólares no satisface el enunciado.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">3&#160;840&#160;000 dólares<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Para 150 unidades, el costo en pesos es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4800</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>150</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>720&#160;000</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> pesos. Después, la conversión correcta a dólares es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>720&#160;000</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>800</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>900</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> dólares. Entonces, 3&#160;840&#160;000 dólares no coincide con el costo solicitado.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Reemplazar la cantidad de unidades en la fórmula</strong></p>
            <p>La fórmula del costo total en pesos chilenos es:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>C</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4800</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mi>u</m:mi>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Como se fabrican <m:math><m:mn>150</m:mn></m:math> unidades, se reemplaza <m:math><m:mi>u</m:mi></m:math> por <m:math><m:mn>150</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mi>C</m:mi>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4800</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>150</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Calcular el costo total en pesos chilenos</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>4800</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>·</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>150</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>720&#160;000</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Entonces, fabricar 150 unidades cuesta <strong>720&#160;000 pesos chilenos</strong>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Convertir de pesos chilenos a dólares</strong></p>
            <p>Se sabe que:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                  <m:mtext> dólar estadounidense</m:mtext>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>800</m:mn>
                  <m:mtext> pesos chilenos</m:mtext>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>Para pasar de pesos a dólares, se divide por 800:</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>720&#160;000</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>÷</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>800</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>900</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El costo de fabricar 150 unidades es <strong>900 dólares</strong>.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es <strong>ChoiceB</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>